de.nec.nle.siafu.types.FlatData

  • Packages that use FlatData 
    Package Description
    de.nec.nle.siafu.model
    This package roughly contains all the modelled data objects.
    de.nec.nle.siafu.types
    All the Publishable objects are in here.

    • Uses of FlatData in de.nec.nle.siafu.model

      Methods in de.nec.nle.siafu.model that return FlatData 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      FlatData Place.flatten()
      Flatten out the Place object with the format: de.nec.nle.siafu.model.Place:name#type#latitude#longitude.
      FlatData Position.flatten()
      Flattens the data in this Position object into the form: de.nec.nle.siafu.model.Position:Lat#Lon where Lat and Lon are the latitude and longitude in decimal format.
      FlatData Place.getContext(String ctxName)
      Returns a context variable in FlatData format.
      FlatData Trackable.getContext(String ctxName)
      Retrieve context information from the trackable.
      FlatData Agent.getContext(String ctxName)
      Returns a context variable in FlatData format.

    • Uses of FlatData in de.nec.nle.siafu.types

      Methods in de.nec.nle.siafu.types that return FlatData 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      FlatData BooleanType.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type BooleanType:trueorfalse where content is the boolean encapsulated in the object.
      FlatData EasyTime.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type EasyTime:HH#MM where content is the string encapsulated in the EasyTime object.
      FlatData IntegerNumber.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type IntegerNumber:int where content is the string encapsulated in the IntegerNumber object.
      FlatData FloatNumber.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type FloatNumber:float where content is the string encapsulated in the FloatNumber object.
      FlatData Text.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type Text:string where content is the string encapsulated in the Text object.
      FlatData Publishable.flatten()
      Turns this object into a String that retains all the necessary informationto be rebuilt by the instance.
      FlatData TimePeriod.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type TimePeriod:startHour#startMinute#endHour#endMinute.
      FlatData TextList.flatten()
      Generates a flattened version of the data, of the type TextList:string1#string2#... where each string is each of the strings contained in the list.
      Constructors in de.nec.nle.siafu.types with parameters of type FlatData 
      Constructor and Description
      BooleanType(FlatData flatData)
      Build a BooleanType object by taking the string that follows the ":" delimiter of the flattened data object and making a Boolean out of it.
      EasyTime(FlatData flatData)
      Builds an EasyTime object by taking a FlatData object of the format EasyTime:HH#MM.
      FloatNumber(FlatData flatData)
      Build an DoubleNumber object by taking the number that follows the ":" delimiter of the flattened data object.
      IntegerNumber(FlatData flatData)
      Build an IntegerNumber object by taking the number that follows the ":" delimiter * of the flattened data object.
      Text(FlatData flatData)
      Build a Text object by taking the string that follows the ":" delimiter of the flattened data object.
      TimePeriod(FlatData flatData)
      Builds a TimePeriod object by taking a FlatData object of the format EasyTime:startHH#startMM#endHH#endMM.
